Package: modsite
Type: Package
Title: RNA Modification Site Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Tang", "YH", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "dumplinghao888@gmail.com")
Author: Tang YH [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Tang YH <dumplinghao888@gmail.com>
Description: A production-quality toolkit for RNA modification site analysis.
    Provides multi-sample merging and quality filtering, genomic region annotation
    via GTF/GFF, cross-referencing against known modification databases,
    sample-level summary statistics, sequencing saturation analysis,
    site-level differential modification analysis (t-test, Wilcoxon, and
    Beta-Binomial GLMM with optional dispersion trend estimation),
    feature-level Cauchy Combination Test (CCT) aggregation for gene and
    transcript summaries, metagene profiling across transcript regions,
    and sequence logo visualization.
